bricksdl is a simplified clone of Atari Breakout game
using with SDL 1.2 (Simple DirectMedia Layer) library.

To build on the Ubuntu Linux for examples:

    $ sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2-dev
    $ make
    $ ./bricksdl
    $ make clean

To play:

    Mouse left button down -- Release the ball / Game continue
    Mouse move -- Move the paddle
    Click window close button -- quit game

